S.FORM: == bucacay, bocacay == u siwkay nu nipaluma i cakatakalaway atu i teban a takalaw nu bayu'. u sanek nu nipaluma malaheci tu imelang pasubana i cacudadan a lacul u zuma a cidekay a kamu u sulit nu zuma a kamu u sulit nu Hulam 五指茄 wuchiqie u sulit nu Lipun u sulit nu Amilika saungay misapayu' a cidekay

== bocacay, bocacay == o siwkay no nipaloma i cakatakalaway ato i teban a takalaw no bayo'. o sanek no nipaloma malaheci to imelang pasobana i cacodadan a lacol o zoma a cidekay a kamo o solit no zoma a kamo o solit no Holam 五指茄 wochiqie o solit no Lipon o solit no Amilika saongay misapayo' a cidekay
